d_sunni = {
	color = { 40 160 40 }
	color2 = { 220 220 0 }
	capital = 226
	creation_requires_capital = no
	dignity = 100
	title = CALIPH
	title_female = CALIPHA
	foa = CALIPH_FOA
	short_name = yes
	religion = sunni
	controls_religion = sunni
	allow = {
		conditional_tooltip = {
			trigger = {
				NOT = {
					has_alternate_start_parameter = {
						key = religion_names
						value = random
					}
				}
			}
			custom_tooltip = {
				text = sunni_creation_independent
				hidden_tooltip = {
					in_revolt = no
					OR = {
						independent = yes
						NOT = {
							any_liege = {
								OR = {
									in_revolt = yes
									NOT = {
										religion = sunni
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}
				}
